{"parse":{"title":"Solapuri chaddar","pageid":47168136,"revid":859631548,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <b>Solapuri chaddar</b> also known as a <b>Solapuri chadar</b> (lit: \"Solapuri bed sheet\") is a cotton <a href=\"/wiki/Bed_sheet\" title=\"Bed sheet\">bed sheet</a> made in the <a href=\"/wiki/Solapur\" title=\"Solapur\">Solapur</a> city of the Indian state of <a href=\"/wiki/Maharashtra\" title=\"Maharashtra\">Maharashtra</a>. <sup id=\"cite_ref-TOI_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TOI-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> These <i>chaddars</i> are popular in India where they are manufactured using <a href=\"/wiki/Hand_loom\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hand loom\">hand loom</a>'s and known for their design and durability. <sup id=\"cite_ref-Solapur_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Solapur-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Solapuri chaddars were the first product in Maharashtra to obtain <a href=\"/wiki/Geographical_Indication\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Geographical Indication\">Geographical Indication</a> (GI) status.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Solapuri_chaddar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Solapur\" title=\"Solapur\">Solapur</a> is known for its textile industry. Once it had Asia's largest <a href=\"/wiki/Cotton_mill\" title=\"Cotton mill\">spinning mills</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TOI_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TOI-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The development of the handloom weaving industry in Solapur seems to have commenced during the regime of the <a href=\"/wiki/Peshwa\" title=\"Peshwa\">Peshwas</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Solapur_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Solapur-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> There were numerous small independent artisan weavers in the industry. Each artisan-house had one or two looms which were generally handled by the head of the family. The family was the unit of work and the women and the children helped the weaver in preparatory processes and in some cases in dyeing also. The rise of the modern factory in India in the 1970s altered the organisation of the local hand-loom weaving industry.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Solapur_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Solapur-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Saptahik_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Saptahik-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\nManufactured by padmashali weavers from South India since their presence in solapur from 1950's. There are many textiles as on today who manufactures chaddars in Solapur district namely Pulgam textiles, Singam Textiles, etc. <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Export\">Export</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Solapuri_chaddar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Export\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Apart from <a href=\"/wiki/Maharashtra\" title=\"Maharashtra\">Maharashtra</a>, Solapuri Chaddar has demand in <a href=\"/wiki/Telangana\" title=\"Telangana\">Telangana</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Andhra_Pradesh\" title=\"Andhra Pradesh\">Andhra Pradesh</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Madhya_Pradesh\" title=\"Madhya Pradesh\">Madhya Pradesh</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Gujarat\" title=\"Gujarat\">Gujarat</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Rajasthan\" title=\"Rajasthan\">Rajasthan</a> within India, while it also has demand in <a href=\"/wiki/United_Arab_Emirates\" title=\"United Arab Emirates\">United Arab Emirates</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Kuwait\" title=\"Kuwait\">Kuwait</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/South_Africa\" title=\"South Africa\">South Africa</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/United_states\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"United states\">United states</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/United_Kingdom\" title=\"United Kingdom\">United Kingdom</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Canada\" title=\"Canada\">Canada</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Saptahik_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Saptahik-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Solapuri_chaddar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-TOI-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-TOI_1-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-TOI_1-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Roli Srivastava (12 October 2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/specials/assembly-elections-2014/maharashtra-news/Shindes-losing-ground-like-chaddar-in-Solapur/articleshow/44794881.cms\">\"Shindes losing ground like chaddar in Solapur\"</a>. <i>The Times of India</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">6 July</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Shindes+losing+ground+like+chaddar+in+Solapur.&amp;rft.date=2014-10-12&amp;rft.au=Roli+Srivastava&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fspecials%2Fassembly-elections-2014%2Fmaharashtra-news%2FShindes-losing-ground-like-chaddar-in-Solapur%2Farticleshow%2F44794881.cms&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASolapuri+ch